- Access DNS management panel

**Step 2: Generate DNSSEC Keys**
```bash
# If using BIND
dnssec-keygen -a RSASHA256 -b 2048 -n ZONE csalab.app
dnssec-keygen -f KSK -a RSASHA256 -b 4096 -n ZONE csalab.app
```

**Step 3: Sign Zone**
```bash
dnssec-signzone -A -3 $(head -c 1000 /dev/random | sha1sum | cut -b 1-16) \
  -N INCREMENT -o csalab.app -t csalab.app.zone
```

**Step 4: Upload DS Records to Registrar**
