## Success Metrics

### Technical Metrics
- **Vulnerability Count:** Reduce from 45 findings to <10 within 90 days
- **Critical/High Findings:** Eliminate all within 72 hours
- **Attack Surface:** Reduce exposed endpoints by 80%
- **Detection Time:** Achieve <5 minute alert time for attacks

### Operational Metrics
- **Patch Cycle:** Establish 30-day patch cycle for all components
