✅ **BREACH Attack**: Likely **LOW RISK** in practice - requires very specific exploitation conditions rarely met in real-world scenarios. Modern browsers and applications have mitigations.

✅ **Wildcard Certificate**: **NOT A VULNERABILITY** - This is standard practice and acceptable when properly managed.

✅ **Cloudflare Detection**: **POSITIVE SECURITY CONTROL** - Not a vulnerability; actually provides protection.

✅ **HTTP/3 Support**: **NOT A VULNERABILITY** - Modern protocol support.

---

