## Executive Context

This section presents the technical security findings identified during the penetration test of `https://dvwa.csalab.app`. Findings are organized by severity level and include detailed technical analysis, evidence, impact assessment, and remediation guidance.

**Critical Note**: The target application is Damn Vulnerable Web Application (DVWA), an intentionally vulnerable training platform. Many findings are expected by design. However, this report treats all findings as if discovered in a production environment to demonstrate proper security assessment methodology.

